1 (c) If a State contract contains a provision listed under subsection (b) of this
2 section, the provision is void ab initio and the contract containing that provision shall be
3 enforceable as if it did not contain the provision.
4 (d) A State contract that contains a provision listed under subsection (b) of this
5 section shall be governed by and construed in accordance with State law, notwithstanding
6 any term or condition to the contrary in the contract.
7 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
8 October 1, 2025.

